snippet.textDisplay:
That audience would laugh at a cripple being sneezed on. Thank God the US took Corden in. He is obnoxious beyond reason. This is the reason late night is a joke. We've lost Craig, but at least we still have Conan. <3


PS. The reason people are angry is because the concept of the bit is, "I drive while my guest and I sing karaoke." but when you can't even pull something that simple off without faking it, then what else is bullshit? Corden's rebuttal reminded me of ProJared's lol...
